00:29:22,794 --> 00:29:23,895
Could all these

276
00:29:23,895 --> 00:29:25,830
possibly be illusions created by settings?

277
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:27,098
You didn't take good care of me.

278
00:29:27,098 --> 00:29:28,166
You left me behind.

279
00:29:28,166 --> 00:29:29,868
That's very irresponsible.

280
00:29:31,136 --> 00:29:32,337
I'm sorry.

281
00:29:43,799 --> 00:29:50,943
