286
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:08,575
♫ A beginning with no end ♫

287
00:30:08,575 --> 00:30:12,895
♫ If we must pursue who's at fault ♫

288
00:30:12,895 --> 00:30:18,614
♫ Blame it all on me ♫

289
00:30:18,614 --> 00:30:22,495
♫ Since words of love are spoken
without a second thought ♫

290
00:30:22,495 --> 00:30:26,555
♫ Why can't I let go with ease ♫

291
00:30:26,555 --> 00:30:33,087
